20:10.417 --> 20:12.667
-Work period everyone.

20:12.709 --> 20:14.959
-Work period.

20:17.417 --> 20:19.458
-Work period.

20:20.750 --> 20:23.875
Yeah?
-Why are you wet sir?

20:27.375 --> 20:29.333
-[Dwyer sighs]

20:31.125 --> 20:33.417
-Alright, we're not going
to do work today.

20:33.458 --> 20:35.583
We are going to...

20:35.625 --> 20:38.125
Play a little game called
Heads Up. Seven Up.

20:38.166 --> 20:40.959
-[Students cheer]
-Sssshhhhh!

20:43.959 --> 20:47.417
So shut your eyes.
Put your heads on your desk.

20:47.458 --> 20:49.417
And let's play.

20:50.583 --> 20:53.500
-Sir, aren't you supposed to
pick seven people?

20:53.542 --> 20:55.750
-Yeah, we're not doing
that part today, okay?

20:59.417 --> 21:02.458
[Gerry whispers]: Never, ever
mix your coolers.

21:02.500 --> 21:05.000
[♪ Music]
-[Gerry whispers]: Too many
fruity flavours.

21:05.959 --> 21:10.417
